CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1941, pg. 18 reads: "Pictures above are of the beautiful South Park Golf Course where the Pittsburgh Elks' Western Pennsylvania Open Golf Tournament will be played June 17.
